Sync Journals Bib
*****************

This manual documents ‘sync-journals-bib’, an Emacs Lisp package that
reconciles the journal field values of a master BibTeX file with the
abbreviation table used by ‘org-ref’ and the official abbreviation table
on the CASSI website.

