3 Configuration
***************

The package exposes four customizable variables.

‘sync-journals-bib-file’
     Path to the master BibTeX file.  The default is
     ‘~/Documents/global.bib’.

‘sync-journals-bib-cassi-url’
     URL of a CASSI search result page.  The default points at the URL
     supplied by the package author.

‘sync-journals-bib-buffer-name’
     Name of the output buffer.  The default is ‘*sync-journals-bib*’.

‘sync-journals-bib-fetch-timeout’
     Number of seconds to wait for the CASSI page to download.  The
     default is 30.


