6 Functions
***********

The internal helpers are documented for completeness.  They are not part
of the public API and may change without notice.

 -- Function: sync-journals-bib--journals-in-file bibfile
     Return a sorted list of unique journal names found in BIBFILE.

 -- Function: sync-journals-bib--normalize s
     Normalize string S for case-insensitive comparison.

 -- Function: sync-journals-bib--known-journals
     Return the list of full journal names known to org-ref.

 -- Function: sync-journals-bib--missing-journals &optional bibfile
     Return journal names in BIBFILE that are absent from org-ref.

 -- Function: sync-journals-bib--build-snippet full-name &optional
          cassi-abbrev key
     Return a formatted ‘add-to-list’ form.

 -- Function: sync-journals-bib--parse-cassi-html html
     Return an alist of (FULL-TITLE .  CAS-ABBREV) pulled from HTML.


